original_title: Timeline: The History of ECW - 1997 - As Told by Sabu
overview: Kayfabe Commentaries brings you that explores the history of harcore year by year.  From the producers of 'Timeline The History of WWE' comes this journey through all the major ECW moments in the ring and behind the scenes. Told by those that were there.
title: Timeline: The History of ECW - 1997 - As Told by Sabu
